something like this?

50:05.654 --> 50:07.874
I know you were hunting
with Sal.

50:10.094 --> 50:13.053
The coroner told me that...

50:15.838 --> 50:18.015
...that she'd been dead
for two days.

50:21.496 --> 50:24.760
I know you didn't
pull the trigger.

50:25.805 --> 50:28.634
But you know who did.

50:28.677 --> 50:30.505
Don't you?

50:33.987 --> 50:35.597
Yeah.

50:35.641 --> 50:38.383
