if you let me go.

50:39.732 --> 50:42.691
Well, that's not the way
we do things around here, son.

51:30.174 --> 51:32.089
Where you going?

51:33.264 --> 51:35.570
I can't be here right now.

51:36.223 --> 51:39.139
But you let me know
the second he wakes up.

51:39.183 --> 51:41.359
- Sure. Why would --
- Brad.

51:41.402 --> 51:43.839
I'll be back in a few.

51:43.883 --> 51:47.234
