59:36.877 --> 59:40.446
Jesus fucking Christ, man.

59:40.489 --> 59:42.056
Nick?

59:42.666 --> 59:44.798
Oh, what the fuck?

59:46.147 --> 59:47.540
Nick.

59:47.584 --> 59:50.717
What the fuck
happened to you, man?

59:50.761 --> 59:52.414
Where you been?

59:53.154 --> 59:55.548
They had me at the hospital.

59:55.592 --> 59:58.029
In the hospital?

59:58.072 --> 01:00:00.988
No, man.
I went there, and...

01:00:01.032 --> 01:00:02.555
cop says you weren't there, man.

01:00:02.599 --> 01:00:04.209
You alright?

01:00:04.252 --> 01:00:06.037
Yeah.

01:00:06.080 --> 01:00:08.735
Oh, shit, man.
I'm so sorry.

01:00:13.522 --> 01:00:15.002
I heard about Tara.

01:00:16.090 --> 01:00:17.744
What'd you hear?

01:00:23.228 --> 01:00:25.056
