that you killed her, man,

01:00:25.099 --> 01:00:27.145
but I know that's bullshit, man.

01:00:27.188 --> 01:00:29.451
Hey, look at me.
I know that's bullshit.

01:00:31.540 --> 01:00:33.760
You know who did it?

01:00:33.804 --> 01:00:36.284
