wanna pick this up.

01:16:08.999 --> 01:16:10.261
This is Frank.

01:16:10.304 --> 01:16:12.263
Frank, Jordan Murray here.

01:16:12.306 --> 01:16:13.743
I was just telling Brad

01:16:13.786 --> 01:16:16.746
